<p>page 83 
</p>
<p>Para. Country Date Type Mandate Allegations transmitted Government response 
means to conduct regular monitoring of all 
psychiatric hospitals. In practice it has been found 
that many hospitals still have a large number of 
cage beds and continue to use them. 
</p>
